definitions.definition: Any carangoid fish of the genus Trachurus , especially Trachurus trachurus , of Europe and America, and Trachurus picturatus of California; the skipjack , scad or horse mackerel .

main_definition: Any carangoid fish of the genus Trachurus , especially Trachurus trachurus , of Europe and America, and Trachurus picturatus of California; the skipjack , scad or horse mackerel .
